version_description: Based off the acoustic demo by Noel on the (What's The Story) Morning Glory? Deluxe Edition.
Electric Guitar with Overdrive/Distortion,Delay and Compression effects play open chords for best effect,if playing on acoustic you can make this rock track sound more like a folk tune.
From the album dig out your soul,written by Liam Gallagher,play with electric guitar ,overdrive and compression effects,gain turned slightly down.
